Context: The George Brown College Alumni Raffle allows individuals to sign up for a monthly raffle by filling out a form with their key details. Participants will be kept informed about application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, and tours. Verified alumni winners will be contacted directly. The contact information provided for inquiries is alumni@georgebrown.ca and the phone numbers 416-415-2000 and TTY: 1-877-515-5559. The college's social media hub can also be visited for additional information. It is important to note that students are responsible for verifying their own George Brown College fee requirements, as the information on the website may change without notice and should not be considered a warranty or representation.
